# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok chancellor angela merkel met with energy industry executives monday , starting long-term talks on securing future supplies amid concern about europe 's dependence on russian and middle eastern oil and gas and sharp disagreements over the role of nuclear power .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (m / meet-03
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Angela"
                        :op2 "Merkel")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (c / chancellor)))
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (ii / industry
                              :mod (e / energy))
                        :ARG2 (e2 / executive)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m2 / monday)))
      :op2 (s / start-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (t / talk-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / secure-01
                        :ARG1 (s3 / supply-01
                              :time (f / future)))
                  :ARG1-of (l / long-03))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (c3 / concern-01
                        :ARG0 (d2 / depend-01
                              :ARG0 (c4 / continent
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Europe"))
                              :ARG1 (a2 / and
                                    :op1 (a3 / and
                                          :op1 (o / oil)
                                          :op2 (g / gas)
                                          :source (w / world-region
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Middle"
                                                      :op2 "East")))
                                    :op2 w)
                              :op3 (d3 / disagree-01
                                    :ARG2 (r / role
                                          :poss (p3 / power
                                                :mod (n4 / nucleus)))
                                    :ARG1-of (s4 / sharp-02)))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :ARG2 (o / official
                        :mod (s2 / senior))))

            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (l / lobby-01
                        :ARG1 (f / favor-01
                              :ARG1 (w2 / whaling)))
                  :op2 (l2 / lobby-01
                        :ARG1 (o2 / oppose-01
                              :ARG1 (w3 / whaling))))
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (e / end-01
                        :ARG0 a
                        :ARG1 (d / disagree-01
                              :ARG0 a
                              :ARG1-of (a3 / acrimony-00)
                              :time (y / year
                                    :mod (r / recent))))
                  :op2 (p2 / pursue-01
                        :ARG0 a
                        :ARG1 (s3 / solve-01
                              :ARG1 (k / kill-01
                                    :ARG0 (c / country
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "Japan"))
                                    :ARG1 (w4 / whale)
                                    :frequency (r2 / rate-entity-91
                                          :ARG3 (t / temporal-quantity
                                                :quant 1
                                                :unit (y2 / year))))
                              :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG2 (d2 / diplomatic)
                                    :ARG3 (m / more))))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

                        :ARG1 (a2 / airline)
                        :ARG2 (p / place-01

                                          :ARG2 (o2 / officer

                                          :ARG1-of (a3 / arm-01)))

                                    :mod (c / certain))

                                          :mod (c2 / commerce))

      :snt1 (c / close-01

                  :mod (s / stock)
                  :mod (c2 / component)

                        :ARG1 (s2 / stock)
                        :location (c3 / city
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Shenzhen"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (f / friday)))
      :snt2 (p / point
            :time d
            :weekday f)
      :ARG1-of (d2 / down-03))
